
Ranger Help for: carve torch
============================

SYNTAX:      carve torch
USAGE:       forest,jungle,swamp,plains
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     10 sp
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to carve of a torch from any wooded area.
The Ranger must have a slash type weapon in order to carve the torch,
and how long the torch lasts depends on how wise a Ranger is. Whether
or not the Ranger knows whats kinds of woods are better than others,
things like what shape makes a good torch.

